reviewText: This video would have been fine if Ms. Patel Thompson didn't go off on an anti-vaccination rant in the middle of the film. All the exercises were helpful, but I didn't need the dose of conspiracist crankery squeezed in among them.

I was a little skeptical about this product, but thought I would give it a try. We have had pretty good success using the techniques in this video. I would suggest it to any parents that have a baby with gas troubles.
